{"tha-ap244:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap244:0.2":"Tuvaradayakavagga ","tha-ap244:0.3":"Nagakesariyattheraapadana ","tha-ap244:1.1":"“Dhanum advejjham katvana, ","tha-ap244:1.2":"vanamajjhogahim aham; ","tha-ap244:1.3":"Kesaram ogatam disva, ","tha-ap244:1.4":"patapattam samutthitam. ","tha-ap244:2.1":"Ubho hatthehi paggayha, ","tha-ap244:2.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","tha-ap244:2.3":"Buddhassa abhiropesim, ","tha-ap244:2.4":"tissassa lokabandhuno. ","tha-ap244:3.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap244:3.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap244:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap244:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap244:4.1":"Tesattatimhi kappamhi, ","tha-ap244:4.2":"satta kesaranamaka; ","tha-ap244:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap244:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap244:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap244:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap244:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap244:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nagakesariyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap244:7.1":"Nagakesariyattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}